Label: PGK_short
Description: PKG_short: Probability of being in Green Zone of Kobe Space (SB>SBMSY & F<FMSY) in Years 1-10 (2024-2033)

Label: PGK_med
Description: PKG_med: Probability of being in Green Zone of Kobe Space (SB>SBMSY & F<FMSY) in Years 11-20 (2034-2043)

Label: PGK_long
Description: PGK_long: Probability of being in Green Zone of Kobe Space (SB>SBMSY & F<FMSY) in Years 21-30 (2044-2053)

Label: nLRP_short
Description: nLRP_short: Probability of not breaching the limit reference point (SSB>0.4SSB_MSY) in any of the first 10 years (2024-2033)

Label: nLRP_med
Description: nLRP_med: Probability of not breaching the limit reference point (SSB>0.4SSB_MSY) in any of years 11-20 (2034-2043)

Label: nLRP_long
Description: nLRP_long: Probability of not breaching the limit reference point (SSB>0.4SSB_MSY) n any of years 21-30 (2044-2053))

Label: rAvTAC_short
Description: rAvTAC_short: Median TAC (t) over years 1-10 relative to the highest median TAC in this period

Label: rAvTAC_med
Description: rAvTAC_med: Median TAC (t) over years 11-20 relative to the highest medianTAC in this period

Label: rAvTAC_long
Description: rAvTAC_long: Median TAC (t) over years 21-30 relative to the highest medianTAC in this period
